#: ../../../reference/maskedarray.generic.rst:440
msgid "Operations on masked arrays"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/maskedarray.generic.rst:442
msgid ""
"Arithmetic and comparison operations are supported by masked arrays. As much "
"as possible, invalid entries of a masked array are not processed, meaning "
"that the corresponding :attr:`~MaskedArray.data` entries *should* be the "
"same before and after the operation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/maskedarray.generic.rst:448
msgid ""
"We need to stress that this behavior may not be systematic, that masked data "
"may be affected by the operation in some cases and therefore users should "
"not rely on this data remaining unchanged."
msgstr ""

